		"description": "<p><strong>Reach 4 | 1d6 + INT damage</strong></p><p>Deal extra damage equal to the sum of the Mana Dice rolled and push a Medium or smaller target 1 space for each Mana Die.</p><p><strong>Upgrades:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Kinetic Redirect.</strong> (1/round) Move the target any direction instead of just away.</li><li><strong>Paired Resonators.</strong> Gain Dual Wielding.</li><li><strong>Extended Arc Coils.</strong> Gain Reach 6 instead.</li></ul><p><strong>Mishap — Recoil:</strong> You are also knocked back the same distance, landing Prone.</p><p><em>Selecting this invention adds the matching item to your inventory; the item itself carries the attack/defense effects and upgrades.</em></p>",
